basics.summary: Laine was born and raised in the Seattle area, graduated from the University of Washington with a BA in Economics.  Laine's interest in high-tech and computers led him to pursue a career in that field which currently spans over 30 years in roles ranging from sales rep, SE, PS Manager, and regional technology specialist.

work.summary: Dell | EMC is a global leader in enabling businesses and service providers to transform their operations and deliver information technology as a service (ITaaS). Fundamental to this transformation is cloud computing. Through innovative products and services, EMC accelerates the journey to cloud computing, helping IT departments to store, manage, protect and analyze their most valuable asset — information — in a more agile, trusted and cost-efficient way.
highlights: Account SE for named commercial accounts in Washington
Successfully won several large "red zone" projects
Led weekly "storage basics" workshops for AEs
